    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000960/extras/9e855cf7cffdb2130d72102a5b5eeb53.avif?t=1770375631\" width=600 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vampdoll: The Blood-Drinking Maidens</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...They are girls who can only survive by drinking the blood of other girls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To exterminate the monstrous beings known as &quot;Werewolves&quot;,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >they fight as part of the Imperial Army's Special Assault Unit, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >code-named &quot;Dog Killers: the Stray Dog Carnag&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As their &quot;rations&quot;, they are provided with girls known as &quot;Bride Thorns&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game is a &quot;yuri&quot; girls' love story, where you witness the emotions between girls who have become vampires and their human partners. </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><strong>What endings will they each choose...?</strong> <br><br>This work is a work of fiction. It is in no way related to any real person or group incident.<br>This work contains some depictions of bloodshed, combat, violence, and emotional romantic scenes.<br>All characters appearing in this work are adults.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Synopsis</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The era is Meiji.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sana Shirafuji, who lost her grandmother and is left alone in the world,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >knocks on the military's door to become a &quot;Bride Thorn&quot; to make a living.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A &quot;Bride Thorn&quot; is a &quot;ration&quot; for girls known as &quot;Vampdolls&quot;,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >who are specialized in combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unaware of this, Sana accepts the military contract out of desperation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On her first day of enlistment, she meets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yukine Hanafusa, a beautiful yet disdainful Vampdoll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gradually, Sana and Yukine begin to understand each other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the first night of blood drinking,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >they discover that the act of drinking blood brings physical and emotional exhilaration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Despite their awkwardness, they experience their first blood drinking together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some time later, Yukine becomes incapacitated during a certain operation...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sana Shirafuji</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000960/extras/4182b16cbfcbe6e5151ada98e8f6212b.avif?t=1770375631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000960/extras_big/4182b16cbfcbe6e5151ada98e8f6212b.avif?t=1770375631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yukine Hanafusa</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000960/extras/3109880acc2e5e18dd5f61dc33df0e4d.avif?t=1770375631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000960/extras_big/3109880acc2e5e18dd5f61dc33df0e4d.avif?t=1770375631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ao Shinokura</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span 